{
  "video_id": "b4k-KPELNcc",
  "title": "Could fish social networks help us save coral reefs? | Mike Gil",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13160.0,
      "end_time": 16840.0,
      "text": "Who here is fascinated by life under the sea?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18960.0,
      "end_time": 20336.0,
      "text": "Fantastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20360.0,
      "end_time": 21919.0,
      "text": "Now, what did we just do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22760.0,
      "end_time": 24576.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s dissect this for a second."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24600.0,
      "end_time": 28960.0,
      "text": "The simple action of an individual raising a hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28120.0,
      "end_time": 29960.0,
      "text": "led many others to do the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30880.0,
      "end_time": 34216.0,
      "text": "Now, it&#39;s true that when individuals in a social network"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34240.0,
      "end_time": 35816.0,
      "text": "have common priorities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35840.0,
      "end_time": 38816.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s often beneficial to copy one another."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38840.0,
      "end_time": 42696.0,
      "text": "Think back to grade school and dressing like the cool kids made you \"cool.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42720.0,
      "end_time": 46416.0,
      "text": "But copying behavior is also common in wild animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46440.0,
      "end_time": 50175.0,
      "text": "For example, some birds copy the alarm calls of other birds"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50200.0,
      "end_time": 53000.0,
      "text": "to spread information about approaching predators."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53920.0,
      "end_time": 57176.0,
      "text": "But could copying behavior in wild animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57200.0,
      "end_time": 60840.0,
      "text": "affect entire ecosystems that we humans depend on?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62400.0,
      "end_time": 64616.0,
      "text": "I was led to this question while studying coral reefs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64640.0,
      "end_time": 68136.0,
      "text": "which support millions of people through fisheries and tourism"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68160.0,
      "end_time": 70735.0,
      "text": "here in Africa and around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 70760.0,
      "end_time": 74160.0,
      "text": "But coral reefs depend on fish"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 74400.0,
      "end_time": 77120.0,
      "text": "that perform a critical job by eating algae."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77640.0,
      "end_time": 78896.0,
      "text": "Because if left unchecked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 78920.0,
      "end_time": 82816.0,
      "text": "these algae can kill coral and take over entire coral reefs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82840.0,
      "end_time": 87440.0,
      "text": "a costly change that is difficult or impossible to reverse."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88160.0,
      "end_time": 91176.0,
      "text": "So to understand how fish may prevent this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 91200.0,
      "end_time": 93136.0,
      "text": "I spy on them"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 93160.0,
      "end_time": 95216.0,
      "text": "while they&#39;re eating algae,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 95240.0,
      "end_time": 97295.0,
      "text": "which can be difficult for them to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97320.0,
      "end_time": 101136.0,
      "text": "in open parts of the reef exposed to predators,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 101160.0,
      "end_time": 102936.0,
      "text": "some of which, on rare occasion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 102960.0,
      "end_time": 105360.0,
      "text": "appear to realize I&#39;m watching them."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 105880.0,
      "end_time": 109920.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 112280.0,
      "end_time": 115336.0,
      "text": "So clearly, clearly, for reef fish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 115360.0,
      "end_time": 117696.0,
      "text": "dining out can be scary."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 117720.0,
      "end_time": 120256.0,
      "text": "But I wanted to understand how these fish do their job"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 120280.0,
      "end_time": 121856.0,
      "text": "in risky situations."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 121880.0,
      "end_time": 126136.0,
      "text": "So my colleagues and I put massive video camera stands"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 126160.0,
      "end_time": 127496.0,
      "text": "in a coral reef"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 127520.0,
      "end_time": 130216.0,
      "text": "to remotely monitor entire feeding grounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 130240.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131816.0,
      "text": "that produce a lot of algae"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 131840.0,
      "end_time": 134600.0,
      "text": "but are exposed to predators."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 135560.0,
      "end_time": 137696.0,
      "text": "And this perspective from above"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 137720.0,
      "end_time": 141216.0,
      "text": "shows us the feeding behavior and precise movements"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 141240.0,
      "end_time": 142816.0,
      "text": "of many different fish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 142840.0,
      "end_time": 144480.0,
      "text": "shown here with colored dots."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 145240.0,
      "end_time": 148136.0,
      "text": "And by analyzing thousands of fish movements"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 148160.0,
      "end_time": 150376.0,
      "text": "to and from feeding grounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 150400.0,
      "end_time": 152000.0,
      "text": "we discovered a pattern."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 152680.0,
      "end_time": 155336.0,
      "text": "These fish, despite being from different species"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 155360.0,
      "end_time": 157176.0,
      "text": "and not swimming in schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 157200.0,
      "end_time": 159215.0,
      "text": "were copying one another,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 159240.0,
      "end_time": 162456.0,
      "text": "such that one fish entering these dangerous feeding grounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 162480.0,
      "end_time": 164880.0,
      "text": "could lead many others to do the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 165320.0,
      "end_time": 168256.0,
      "text": "And fish stayed for longer and ate more algae"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 168280.0,
      "end_time": 171296.0,
      "text": "when they were surrounded by more feeding fish."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 171320.0,
      "end_time": 173256.0,
      "text": "Now, this could be happening"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 173280.0,
      "end_time": 175856.0,
      "text": "because even simple movements by individual fish"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 175880.0,
      "end_time": 179856.0,
      "text": "can inadvertently communicate vital information."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 179880.0,
      "end_time": 183856.0,
      "text": "For example, if even one fish sees a predator and flees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 183880.0,
      "end_time": 186616.0,
      "text": "this can alert many others to danger."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 186640.0,
      "end_time": 190559.0,
      "text": "And a fish safely entering feeding grounds can show others that the coast is clear."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 191320.0,
      "end_time": 195335.0,
      "text": "So it turns out that even when these fish are different species,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 195360.0,
      "end_time": 198976.0,
      "text": "they are connected within social networks"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 199000.0,
      "end_time": 202000.0,
      "text": "which can provide information on when it&#39;s safe to eat."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 202840.0,
      "end_time": 207816.0,
      "text": "And our analyses indicate that fish simply copying other fish in their social network"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 207840.0,
      "end_time": 212896.0,
      "text": "could account for over 60 percent of the algae eaten by the fish community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 212920.0,
      "end_time": 217935.0,
      "text": "and thus could be critical to the flow of energy and resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 217960.0,
      "end_time": 219960.0,
      "text": "through coral reef ecosystems."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 220680.0,
      "end_time": 223256.0,
      "text": "But these findings also suggest that overfishing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 223280.0,
      "end_time": 225256.0,
      "text": "a common problem in coral reefs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 225280.0,
      "end_time": 227736.0,
      "text": "not only removes fish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 227760.0,
      "end_time": 230816.0,
      "text": "but it could break up the social network of remaining fish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 230840.0,
      "end_time": 233616.0,
      "text": "which may hide more and eat less algae"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 233640.0,
      "end_time": 236176.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re missing critical information."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 236200.0,
      "end_time": 240160.0,
      "text": "And this would make coral reefs more vulnerable than we currently predict."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 242400.0,
      "end_time": 246376.0,
      "text": "So remarkably, fish social networks"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 246400.0,
      "end_time": 249296.0,
      "text": "allow the actions of one to spread to many"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 249320.0,
      "end_time": 251256.0,
      "text": "and could affect entire coral reefs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 251280.0,
      "end_time": 254536.0,
      "text": "which feed millions of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 254560.0,
      "end_time": 256336.0,
      "text": "and support the global economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 256360.0,
      "end_time": 257840.0,
      "text": "for all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 258440.0,
      "end_time": 261136.0,
      "text": "Now, our discovery points us towards better ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 261160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263336.0,
      "text": "to sustainably manage coral reefs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 263360.0,
      "end_time": 264936.0,
      "text": "but it also shows us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 264960.0,
      "end_time": 269135.0,
      "text": "we humans are not just affected by the actions of other humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 269160.0,
      "end_time": 272550.0,
      "text": "but we could be affected by the actions of individual fish"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 272790.0,
      "end_time": 273856.0,
      "text": "on a distant coral reef"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 273880.0,
      "end_time": 276336.0,
      "text": "through their simple copying behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 276360.0,
      "end_time": 277576.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 277600.0,
      "end_time": 282320.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}